<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="45" type="comments">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="45">Comments:</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="45">
This genus is named in honor of the late Steven L. Wood, Monte L. Bean Life Science Museum, Brigham Young University, Provo, Utah, USA, the preeminent authority on the systematics and taxonomy of the 
<taxonomicName family="Scolytidae" lsidName="" pageId="0" pageNumber="45" rank="family">Scolytidae</taxonomicName>
. Dr. Wood was my major professor while I was a graduate student at Brigham Young University many years ago, and remained a valued colleague until his death in July 2009.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
